data.description: Welcome to your mountain getaway or second home! This property offers the perfect combination of breathtaking views and outdoor fun. With Hollydot Golfcourse, San Isabel Lake, Lake Beckwith, and Rye Recreation Center all nearby, you'll never run out of things to do. Enjoy panoramic vistas from every angle with oversized picture windows and decks at either end of the house. Relax after a day outdoors in front of one of the three wood burning fireplaces or host family retreats in the formal dining room. The large eat-in kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances including a built-in glass cooktop stove. Additionally, this home has a lower level family room that walks out to a covered patio as well as its own summer kitchen/mudroom with exterior entrance—perfect for multi-family living! Natural mountain landscaping ensures low maintenance while new roofing, perimeter fencing, hot water heat system (maintained regularly), pump on private well, and newly cleaned septic tank make this an incredibly desirable property. Plus it's now on natural gas so you can take advantage of even more convenience! Don't miss out on experiencing small community living in this beautiful open space—make it yours today!
